<item>
            <title>[FLINK-21655] Incorrect simplification for coalesce call on a groupingsets&apos; result</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-21655</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the planner will do an incorrectly simplification for `coalesce` call on a `groupingsets`&apos;s result, see the following query example:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-scala&quot;&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; sqlQuery =
 &quot;&quot;&quot;
 |SELECT
 | a,
 | b,
 | coalesce(c, &apos;empty&apos;),
 | avg(d)
 |FROM t1
 |GROUP BY GROUPING SETS ((a, b), (a, b, c))
 &quot;&quot;&quot;.stripMargin

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;will generate a wrong plan which lost the `coalesce` call:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;

Calc(select=[a, b, c AS EXPR$2, EXPR$3])
+- HashAggregate(isMerge=[&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;], groupBy=[a, b, c, $e], select=[a, b, c, $e, Final_AVG(sum$0, count$1) AS EXPR$3])
 +- Exchange(distribution=[hash[a, b, c, $e]])
 +- LocalHashAggregate(groupBy=[a, b, c, $e], select=[a, b, c, $e, Partial_AVG(d) AS (sum$0, count$1)])
 +- Expand(projects=[\{a, b, c, d, 0 AS $e}, \{a, b, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt; AS c, d, 1 AS $e}])
 +- TableSourceScan(table=[[default_catalog, default_database, t1]], fields=[a, b, c, d])

&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
